The following issue went on sale today:  Issuer:      Cablevision Systems
Manager(s):  Bank of America Merrill Lynch  Barclays Capital  BNP Paribas  Credit Agricole
Amount:      $750 million
Coupon:      5.875 percent
Maturity:    Sept. 15, 2022
Settlement:  Sept. 27, 2012
Spread:      415 basis points more than governments
 